<l>makaṉ tantaik kāṟṟu mutavi yivaṉṟantai</l>
<l>yeṉṉōṟṟāṉ kolleṉuñ col</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(So to act) that it may be said "by what great penance did his father beget him," is the benefit which a son should render to his father.</l>
